OL,3,CMan charged with rape following car
OL,4,Cpark attack
OL,6,FA 27-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith rape following an investigation
OL,8,Finto an attack in a West Sussex car
OL,9,Fpark.
OL,11,FThe incident took place in the
OL,12,FLyndhurst Road car park in Worthing at
OL,13,Fapproximately 8:00pm on Wednesday,
OL,14,FMarch 11.
OL,16,FSussex Police confirmed that Suleman
OL,17,FMukaish, of Cambridge Road, Worthing,
OL,18,Fhas been charged with the offence.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
