OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773745530
OL,3,CMan charged with rape following car
OL,4,Cpark attack
OL,6,FHe has been remanded in custody and to
OL,7,Fappear at Crawley Magistrates' Court
OL,8,Ftoday (Monday, March 16).
OL,10,FThe victim, a woman in her 20s,
OL,11,Fcontinues to be supported by
OL,12,Fspecialist officers following the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,FPolice had previously cordoned off the
OL,16,Fcar park to preserve evidence as part
OL,17,Fof 'Operation Blyth'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
