OL,3,CMan charged with rape following car
OL,4,Cpark attack
OL,6,FResidents were told to expect an
OL,7,Fincreased police presence in the area
OL,8,Fwhile detectives carried out fast-
OL,9,Ftrack enquiries.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Sussex Police
OL,12,Fsaid:"This is being treated as an
OL,13,Fisolated incident and police are not
OL,14,Flooking for anybody else in connection
OL,15,Fwith the offence."
